ine-height: 34.2px; position: relative; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"http://www.devstore.cn/essay/essayInfo/3545.html\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 133, 208); text-decoration: none; outline: none medium; transition: all 0.2s ease; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">30条爆笑的程序员梗PHP是最好的语言</a></p><p><br/></p>','一言不合就学习：PHP优秀学习文章资料汇总整理','最近，小编们一直在收集，整理一些针对包括程序员、运营、设计师等在内的系统学习资料，希望给初学者一些参考，也给已经入门的人一些进阶建议，让知识体系 更加系统化。当然，这个工作不可能一蹴而就，也相当不能完善，每天都有新技能、新技术产生，并发生变化，但也希望小编的努力能对大家有些微帮助。','1','1','2016-08-31 11:09:24','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','5','1','0','0','','');
INSERT INTO cmf_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `post_demo_url`, `post_download_url` ) VALUES  ('43','1','','','2016-08-31 11:20:56','<p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(46, 46, 46); white-space: normal; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 宋体, &#39;Myriad Pro&#39;, Lato, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">后来我碰巧<a href=\"https://www.quora.com/Why-are-programmers-obsessed-with-cats\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 153, 204); text-decoration: none; outline: none medium; transition-property: color; transition-duration: 0.3s; transition-timing-function: ease; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">在 Quora 上</a>也看到有讨论程序员和喵星人。有位网友提问：「我很好奇，为什么在程序员的照片、博客中，喵星人出镜率为什么这么高？」。伯乐在线<a href=\"http://www.jobbole.com/members/cnxm\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 153, 204); text-decoration: none; outline: none medium; transition-property: color; transition-duration: 0.3s; transition-timing-function: ease; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">@踏歌行</a>&nbsp;摘译了几位程序员的分享。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(46, 46, 46); white-space: normal; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 宋体, &#39;Myriad Pro&#39;, Lato, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 1em; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Michael Disibio，（一只带猫的 .Net 程序猿）</strong></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(46, 46, 46); white-space: normal; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 宋体, &#39;Myriad Pro&#39;, Lato, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">①喵星人会陪着你敲代码，而你的老婆、你的老板不会。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(46, 46, 46); white-space: normal; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 宋体, &#39;Myriad Pro&#39;, Lato, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">②喵星人会趴在旁边看你敲代码…然后就睡着了（可能是看别人敲代码是件极其享受的事）</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(46, 46, 46); white-space: normal; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 宋体, &#39;Myriad Pro&#39;, Lato, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">③如果被喵星人被屏幕上移动的光标吸引了，它们会去抓光标。当然是什么都抓不到，哈哈（智商感人）。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(46, 46, 46); white-space: normal; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 宋体, &#39;Myriad Pro&#39;, Lato, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">④喵星人喜欢玩键盘。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(46, 46, 46); white-space: normal; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 宋体, &#39;Myriad Pro&#39;, Lato, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">⑤当你离开电脑一会会，回来就会发现喵星人正惬意地躺在你的椅子上，盯着你看，一脸得意，好像在说：“你是不是觉得敲代码简直比猜字谜还痛苦，需要我来告诉你该怎么做嘛？”</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(46, 46, 46); white-space: normal; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 宋体, &#39;Myriad Pro&#39;, Lato, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">⑥跟程序员一样，喵星人也没有固定的吃饭时间，有时间就吃点。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(46, 46, 46); white-space: normal; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 宋体, &#39;Myriad Pro&#39;, Lato, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">⑦衡量喵星人成功的措施和软件类似，与做事情所消耗的能量成反比。（即：喵星人和程序员都很追求效率）</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(46, 46, 46); white-space: normal; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 宋体, &#39;Myriad Pro&#39;, Lato, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">⑧喵星人累了会找个地方睡觉，这点跟程序员很相似。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(46, 46, 46); white-space: normal; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 宋体, &#39;Myriad Pro&#39;, Lato, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">⑨当花了一整晚解决技术难题，即使是在凌晨 4 点，喵星人也会跟你一起庆祝，前提是得给他准备一碗牛奶（吃货）。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(46, 46, 46); white-space: normal; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 宋体, &#39;Myriad Pro&#39;, Lato, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(46, 46, 46); white-space: normal; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 宋体, &#39;Myriad Pro&#39;, Lato, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 1em; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Bruno Skvorc 的回答</strong></p><blockquote style=\"word-wrap: break-word; padding: 10px 20px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; white-space: normal; border-width: 0px 0px 0px 5px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); font-size: 15px; color: rgb(94, 94, 94); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 宋体, &#39;Myriad Pro&#39;, Lato, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border: 0px;\">我先给大家讲个笑话。<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/>有一天，程序员发现一只青蛙，令他惊讶的是这只青蛙竟然会说话。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border: 0px;\">“亲我一下，我就会变成公主。”</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border: 0px;\">程序员没理青蛙，而是把青蛙放到包里走了。走着走着，青蛙又说话了。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border: 0px;\">“你亲我一下，我就会变成公主。或者你让我亲一下，我就让你牵我手牵一天。”</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border: 0px;\">程序员又一次无视了青蛙的话。青蛙开始晓之以理，动之以情。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border: 0px;\">“好吧，你把我变成公主，我就答应做你一星期的女朋友。你甚至可以把我带去向你的朋友们炫耀。”</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border: 0px;\">还是没有回应（沉默…）</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border: 0px;\">“说真的，小伙子，我很&nbsp;hot。你把我变成公主，我就跟你啪啪啪。你可以向朋友们炫耀，我会告诉他们你有多厉害。”</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border: 0px;\">终于，程序员说话了：</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border: 0px;\">“你看，我是个程序员，我根本没时间找女朋友。但有一只会说话的青蛙，真的很酷。”</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border: 0px;\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 1em; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">（译注：程序员内心独白：让我亲一只青蛙，还想让我当她女朋友，还想让我跟她啪啪啪，这只青蛙脑子没病吧？）</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/>喵星人和人很相似，不需要花太多精力去照顾。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border: 0px;\">大部分时间，喵星人会照顾好自己，当它们需要同伴时，它们首先会把自己变成合格的同伴。在你敲代码的时候，它们会在旁边安静的趴着，不吵不闹。当你需要自我交谈来解决那些沉思解决不了的问题时，它们是很好的聆听者。（伯小乐提醒，各位猿媛，你们还记得<a href=\"http://blog.jobbole.com/85719/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 153, 204); text-decoration: none; outline: none medium; transition-property: color; transition-duration: 0.3s; transition-timing-function: ease; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">程序员都要知道的小黄鸭调试法</a>么？喵星人也可以当小黄鸭的呀~）</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border: 0px;\">喵星人非常喜欢干净，每天只要定时打扫喂养就行。喵星人会在你难过的时候安慰你，在你开心的时候陪着你开心，在你不想被打扰的时候默默陪伴你。有喵星人陪着的时候，甚至连恼人的苍蝇、蚊子都没了。这就是一种共生关系。</p></blockquote><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(46, 46, 46); white-space: normal; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 宋体, &#39;Myriad Pro&#39;, Lato, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(46, 46, 46); white-space: normal; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 宋体, &#39;Myriad Pro&#39;, Lato, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 1em; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Jarrod Spillers 的回复</strong></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(46, 46, 46); white-space: normal; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 宋体, &#39;Myriad Pro&#39;, Lato, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">为什么喜欢猫？因为有时候它们会帮你写代码呀！（冬天时）笔记本很暖和舒适，喵星人可以趴键盘上好几个小时呢。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Verdana, 微软雅黑, &#39;Lucida Grande&#39;, &#39;Lucida Sans Unicode&#39;, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"http://www.phpchina.com/data/attachment/portal/201607/21/091100mqas0bdqhasd0zh2.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); text-decoration: none; outline: none medium; transition-property: color; transition-duration: 0.3s; transition-timing-function: ease;\"><img src=\"http://develop.laoit.cn/data/upload/ueditor/20160831/57c64d0a2a6ba.jpg\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: none; vertical-align: middle; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 100%; display: table;\"/></a></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(46, 46, 46); white-space: normal; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 宋体, &#39;Myriad Pro&#39;, Lato, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(46, 46, 46); white-space: normal; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 宋体, &#39;Myriad Pro&#39;, Lato, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">伯小乐再多说几句：开头提到的 maxogden 童鞋，他还有很多猫，如下图。他甚至还给喵星人写了一个教程《JavaScript For Cats》，当然了，这写给 JS 新手的。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Verdana, 微软雅黑, &#39;Lucida Grande&#39;, &#39;Lucida Sans Unicode&#39;, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"http://www.phpchina.com/data/attachment/portal/201607/21/091101v93132r14pm9m2pu.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); text-decoration: none; outline: none medium; transition-property: color; transition-duration: 0.3s; transition-timing-function: ease;\"><img src=\"http://develop.laoit.cn/data/upload/ueditor/20160831/57c64d0a984a4.jpg\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: none; vertical-align: middle; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 100%; display: table;\"/></a></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Verdana, 微软雅黑, &#39;Lucida Grande&#39;, &#39;Lucida Sans Unicode&#39;, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"http://www.phpchina.com/data/attachment/portal/201607/21/091101vxzz4mbox4mhjxg4.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); text-decoration: none; outline: none medium; transition-property: color; transition-duration: 0.3s; transition-timing-function: ease;\"><img src=\"http://develop.laoit.cn/data/upload/ueditor/20160831/57c64d0add244.jpg\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: none; vertical-align: middle; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 100%; display: table;\"/></a></p><p><br/></p>','趣文：为什么有些程序员特别喜欢猫？','后来我碰巧在 Quora 上也看到有讨论程序员和喵星人。有位网友提问：「我很好奇，为什么在程序员的照片、博客中，喵星人出镜率为什么这么高？」。伯乐在线@踏歌行 摘译了几位程序员的分享。','1','1','2016-08-31 11:11:15','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');
