file_get_contents($url);?&gt;</pre><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; line-height: 22.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">php脚本sleep 一段时间之后通过访问自身的方式继续执行. 就好像接力赛跑一样..这样就能保证每个PHP脚本执行时间不会太长. 也就不受time_out的限制了.</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; line-height: 22.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">因为每一次一次循环php文件都是独立执行,所以这种方法,避免了time_out的限制. 但是最好和上边一样 加上控制代码. cofig.php , 以便能够终止进程.</p><h2 id=\"articleHeader3\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 1.75em; font-weight: 500; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">四. 服务器定时任务</h2><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; line-height: 22.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Unix平台</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; line-height: 22.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果您使用 Unix 系统，您需要在您的 PHP 脚本的最前面加上一行特殊的代码，使得它能够被执行，这样系统就能知道用什么样的程序要运行该脚本。为 Unix 系统增加的第一行代码不会影响该脚本在 Windows 下的运行，因此您也可以用该方法编写跨平台的脚本程序。</p><h3 id=\"articleHeader4\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1、在Crontab中使用PHP执行脚本</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; line-height: 22.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">就像在Crontab中调用普通的shell脚本一样（具体Crontab用法），使用PHP程序来调用PHP脚本，每一小时执行 myscript.php 如下：</p><pre class=\"hljs markdown\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; padding: 1em; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; font-size: 0.93em; box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: &#39;Source Code Pro&#39;, Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; line-height: 1.3; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(101, 123, 131); border: none; border-radius: 3px; max-height: 35em; position: relative; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">#&nbsp;crontab&nbsp;-e00&nbsp;*&nbsp;*&nbsp;*&nbsp;*&nbsp;/usr/local/bin/php&nbsp;/home/john/myscript.php</pre><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; line-height: 22.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">/usr/local/bin/php</span>为PHP程序的路径。</p><h3 id=\"articleHeader5\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2、在Crontab中使用URL执行脚本</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; line-height: 22.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果你的PHP脚本可以通过URL触发，你可以使用 lynx 或 curl 或 wget 来配置你的Crontab。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; line-height: 22.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">下面的例子是使用Lynx文本浏览器访问URL来每小时执行PHP脚本。Lynx文本浏览器默认使用对话方式打开URL。但是，像下面的，我们在lynx命令行中使用-dump选项来把URL的输出转换来标准输出。</p><pre class=\"hljs markdown\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; padding: 1em; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; font-size: 0.93em; box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: &#39;Source Code Pro&#39;, Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; line-height: 1.3; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(101, 123, 131); border: none; border-radius: 3px; max-height: 35em; position: relative; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">00&nbsp;*&nbsp;*&nbsp;*&nbsp;*&nbsp;lynx&nbsp;-dump&nbsp;http://www.sf.net/myscript.php</pre><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; line-height: 22.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">下面的例子是使用&nbsp;<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">CURL</span>&nbsp;访问URL来每5分执行PHP脚本。Curl默认在标准输出显示输出。使用 &quot;curl -o&quot; 选项，你也可以把脚本的输出转储到临时文件temp.txt。</p><pre class=\"hljs ruby\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; padding: 1em; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; font-size: 0.93em; box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: &#39;Source Code Pro&#39;, Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; line-height: 1.3; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(101, 123, 131); border: none; border-radius: 3px; max-height: 35em; position: relative; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">*/5&nbsp;*&nbsp;*&nbsp;*&nbsp;*&nbsp;/usr/bin/curl&nbsp;-o&nbsp;temp.txt&nbsp;http://www.sf.net/myscript.php</pre><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; line-height: 22.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">下面的例子是使用WGET访问URL来每10分执行PHP脚本。-q 选项表示安静模式。&quot;-O temp.txt&quot; 表示输出会发送到临时文件。</p><pre class=\"hljs ruby\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; padding: 1em; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; font-size: 0.93em; box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: &#39;Source Code Pro&#39;, Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; line-height: 1.3; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(101, 123, 131); border: none; border-radius: 3px; max-height: 35em; position: relative; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">*/10&nbsp;*&nbsp;*&nbsp;*&nbsp;*&nbsp;/usr/bin/wget&nbsp;-q&nbsp;-O&nbsp;temp.txt&nbsp;http://www.sf.net/myscript.php</pre><h2 id=\"articleHeader6\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 1.75em; font-weight: 500; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">五. ini_set函数用法详解</h2><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; line-height: 22.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">PHP ini_set用来设置php.ini的值，<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">在函数执行的时候生效，脚本结束后，设置失效</span>。无需打开php.ini文件，就能修改配置，对于虚拟空间来说，很方便。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; line-height: 22.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">函数格式：</p><pre class=\"hljs cs\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; padding: 1em; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; font-size: 0.93em; box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: &#39;Source Code Pro&#39;, Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; line-height: 1.3; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(101, 123, 131); border: none; border-radius: 3px; max-height: 35em; position: relative; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">string&nbsp;ini_set(string&nbsp;$varname,&nbsp;string&nbsp;$newvalue)</pre><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; line-height: 22.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">不是所有的参数都可以配置，可以查看手册中的列表。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; line-height: 22.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">常见的设置：</p><pre class=\"hljs css\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; padding: 1em; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; font-size: 0.93em; box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: &#39;Source Code Pro&#39;, Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; line-height: 1.3; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(101, 123, 131); border: none; border-radius: 3px; max-height: 35em; position: relative; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">@&nbsp;ini_set(&#39;memory_limit&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;64M&#39;);</pre><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; line-height: 22.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">menory_limit</span>：设定一个脚本所能够申请到的最大内存字节数，这有利于写的不好的脚本消耗服务器上的可用内存。<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">@符号代表不输出错误</span>。</p><pre class=\"hljs coffeescript\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; padding: 1em; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; font-size: 0.93em; box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: &#39;Source Code Pro&#39;, Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; line-height: 1.3; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(101, 123, 131); border: none; border-radius: 3px; max-height: 35em; position: relative; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">@ini_set(&#39;display_errors&#39;,&nbsp;1);</pre><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; line-height: 22.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">display_errors</span>：设置错误信息的类别。</p><pre class=\"hljs coffeescript\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; padding: 1em; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; font-size: 0.93em; box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: &#39;Source Code Pro&#39;, Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; line-height: 1.3; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(101, 123, 131); border: none; border-radius: 3px; max-height: 35em; position: relative; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">@ini_set(&#39;session.auto_start&#39;,&nbsp;0);</pre><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; line-height: 22.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">session.auto_start</span>：是否自动开session处理，设置为1时，程序中不用session_start()来手动开启session也可使用session，</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; line-height: 22.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果参数为0，又没手动开启session，则会报错。</p><pre class=\"hljs coffeescript\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; padding: 1em; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; font-size: 0.93em; box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: &#39;Source Code Pro&#39;, Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; line-height: 1.3; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(101, 123, 131); border: none; border-radius: 3px; max-height: 35em; position: relative; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">@ini_set(&#39;session.cache_expire&#39;,&nbsp;180);</pre><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; line-height: 22.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">session.cache_expire</span>：指定会话页面在客户端cache中的有限期（分钟）缺省下为180分钟。如果设置了session.cache_limiter=nocache时，此处设置无 效。</p><pre class=\"hljs coffeescript\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; padding: 1em; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; font-size: 0.93em; box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: &#39;Source Code Pro&#39;, Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; line-height: 1.3; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(101, 123, 131); border: none; border-radius: 3px; max-height: 35em; position: relative; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">@ini_set(&#39;session.use_cookies&#39;,&nbsp;1);</pre><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; line-height: 22.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">session.use_cookies</span>：是否使用cookie在客户端保存会话ID；</p><pre class=\"hljs coffeescript\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; padding: 1em; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; font-size: 0.93em; box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: &#39;Source Code Pro&#39;, Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; line-height: 1.3; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(101, 123, 131); border: none; border-radius: 3px; max-height: 35em; position: relative; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">@ini_set(&#39;session.use_trans_sid&#39;,&nbsp;0);</pre><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; line-height: 22.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">session.use_trans_sid</span>：是否使用明码在URL中显示SID（会话ID），</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; line-height: 22.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">默认是禁止的，因为它会给你用户带来安全危险</span>：</p><ol style=\"list-style-type: none;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\">用户可能将包含有效的sid的URL通过email/irc/QQ/MSN等途径告诉其他人。</p></li><li><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\">包含有效sid的URL可能会保存在公用电脑上。</p></li><li><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\">用户可能保存带有固定不变的SID的URL在他们的收藏夹或者浏览历史记录里。 基于URL的会话管理总是比基于Cookie的会话管理有更多的风险，所以应当禁用。</p></li></ol><p><br/></p>','PHP 实现定时任务的几种方法','这几天需要用PHP写一个定时抓取网页的服务器应用. 在网上搜了一下解决办法, 发现OSchina的 一个问题的解答很精彩(值得一看,谢谢大牛们的精彩回答O(∩_∩)O~), 提出几种解决办法.现总结如下.','1','1','2016-08-31 11:33:22','','0','','','1','{\"thumb\":\"20160831\\/57c650af071b6.jpg\"}','6','0','0','0','','');

